NEW This week on #BialikBreakdown 🧠💥 Did you catch last week’s surprise Thursday episode?! 😮 Mayim and Jonathan react to our recent episode with Marc Maron! They reflect on Maron’s vulnerability as he shared about his complicated relationship with his parents, how he turned to music and drugs to cope, and the origins of his anger. They also discuss what happens when we’re denied a fundamental sense of self, the benefits of being raw and open about grief, and using comedy as a tool to transmute pain. Visit ▶️ the link in our bio for the full episode! 🎙🎧 #mayimbialik #mentalhealthpodcast #marcmaron #mentalhealthawareness

So, I sent my boots to @whitesboots to be resoled and they wound up in a photo shoot by coincidence. They were looking for some oldies on the repair rack, I guess. They had no idea they were mine until after. Now I have an amazing pic of my boots. Which isn’t nothing if you like boots. Someday I’ll get my actual boots back. They’ll be different though. They’ll probably have an attitude. #truestory #WhitesSemiDress photo: @dylanspitz
